# Nucleus bundle identifier

Use **`net.suherman.nucleus`** for every Nucleus Apple app target (macOS and iOS).

## Forbidden

- `net.suherman.nucleus.ios` or any other iOS-specific bundle suffix
- Separate WeatherKit / CloudKit / Keychain App IDs for mobile

## Required alignment

- Xcode `PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER`: `net.suherman.nucleus`
- iCloud container: `iCloud.net.suherman.nucleus`
- Keychain access group: `$(AppIdentifierPrefix)net.suherman.nucleus`
- URL scheme / deep links: `net.suherman.nucleus`

Prefer `NucleusAppIdentity.bundleIdentifier` from NucleusCore when referencing the bundle ID in Swift.
